newsitem.title: USA: El Paso Cty SD 3, Colo., yields 5.70 pct in 2021.
newsitem.headline: El Paso Cty SD 3, Colo., yields 5.70 pct in 2021.

text.p: Hanifen, Imhoff Inc said it tentatively priced $ 7.900 million of El Paso County School District No 3 (Widefield), Colo., with a top yield of 5.70 percent.
